  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Drive in the EU after Brexit: lorry and goods vehicle drivers
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    What UK lorry and goods vehicle drivers need to do to drive professionally in the EU if there's a no-deal Brexit.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

